org.svvrl.goal.core.util
Class LatestAppearanceRecord<T>

java.lang.Object
  org.svvrl.goal.core.util.LatestAppearanceRecord<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of elements in the record
Direct Known Subclasses:
NMG2NPG.ParityState
public class LatestAppearanceRecord<T>
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides an implementation of latest appearance records (LAR). This implementation separates the record into a list of elements and an index of the marker.

Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
